Articles.Content:
KSP is kind of bugging me lately. It has an extreme tendency to wanting to crash upon reverting to either "Launch", "Spaceplane Hangar", "VAB"... And it gets worse and worse with mods, and the more I use the game, the WORSE the crashing gets. I have approximately 21 mods, which I absolutely CANNOT live without. I've tried Active Texture Management, and it is now outdated. I've tried deleting some of the outdated mods, and none of it works. Could use some help. I'm going to post one of the billions of all of the error.log files right here (It's big. Sorry.); Unity Player [version: Unity 5.2.4f1_98095704e6fe]
